PASS CAMBRIDGE

BEC Vantage

Audio CD

The CD aims to provide useful audio support for students preparing to take the Cambridge BEC Vantage examination and to those also who aim to earn proficiency in READING, WRITING, LISTENING and SPEAKING ENGLISH.

IT IS NOT NECESSARY THAT ONE PERSON WHO HAS TO GIVE THE BEC EXAM CAN DOWNLOAD THIS FILE. ANYBODY CAN DOWNLOAD AND USE THE FILES AS THIS WILL TEACH YOU ENGLISH FOR FREE.

A Very useful CD with audio tracks to learn from.
